<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
    <%- include('template/head')%>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style_lottery.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('template/navbar')%>
        <% if (!prize || prize<1) { %>
            <section class='background active'>
                <div class='list_table'>
                    <h2 class='list_title'>2020 夏日輕盈特賞！ 抽獎活動辦法</h2>
                    <ul class='list_body'>
                        <li class='list_item'>
                            <div class='item_title'>活動期間：</div>
                            <div class='item_desc'>2020/06/01~2020/07/01</div>
                        </li>
                        <li class='list_item'>
                            <div class='item_title'>活動說明：</div>
                            <div class='item_desc'>今天老闆佛心來著決定給大家發獎勵，有看有機會，沒看只能幫QQ！只要在店內消費滿1000000元即有機會獲得 -
                                頭獎日本東京來回雙人遊！
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class='list_item'>
                            <div class='item_title'>獎  品：</div>
                            <div class='item_desc'>
                                ❤ 頭獎一名：日本東京來回雙人遊(市價14990元)
                                <br />
                                ❤ 貳獎三名：90 吋電視一台(市價5990元)
                                <br />
                                ❤ 參獎十名：知名 YouTuber 簽名握手會入場券一張(市價1500元)
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <button type="button" class='lottery_button'>
                        <a href='/handle_lottery'>我要抽獎</a>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </section>
            <% }else{ %>
                <section class='first_price_background'
                    style='background: url("<%= prize.pic %>") center/cover no-repeat;'>
                    <div class='show_prise'>
                        <%= prize.prize %>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" class='lottery_button'>
                        <a href='/handle_lottery'>我要抽獎</a>
                    </button>
                </section>
                <% } %>
                    <%- include('template/footer')%>
</body>

</html>